<td><b>Abstract</b></td>
<td>
The Calm website provides tools designed to improve mental health through meditation and relaxation. It offers guided sessions, breathing exercises, and sleep support to help users manage stress and anxiety. The platform is easy to use and allows individuals to access mental health support anytime. It is especially useful for people who may not want in-person therapy. However, while Calm is helpful, it should be used as a support tool rather than a replacement for professional treatment.
</td>
