<tr>
<td><b>Abstract</b></td>
<td>
Headspace is a mental health app focused on meditation and mindfulness. It provides structured programs that help users reduce stress, improve focus, and manage anxiety. The app includes features like guided meditation, sleep support, and mood tracking. It makes mental health care more accessible by allowing users to practice these techniques anywhere. While it offers many benefits, it is still important to recognize that it does not replace professional therapy.
</td>
